The Artist

Born, raised and living on the outskirts of the big city of Toronto, Ontario, Canada, with my loving and supportive husband along with our Bernese Mountain Dogs.Â We live alongside the beautiful Rouge Valley and not far from the shores of Lake Ontario the perfect location for lots of dog walking on trails.
